quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Ndarahiye kuri iki gisagara c’Imakkat
  90,2,Na wewe uzomanuka muri iki gisagara nyene
  90,3,"Ndarahiye kukintu cavyaye, hamwe nicavutse"
  90,4,Yuko twaremye ikiremwa muntu mungorane nyinshi cane
  90,5,Mbega yiyumvira yuko ata n’umwe yoshobora kumufata
  90,6,"Avuga ati:- narononye amatungo menshi cane"
  90,7,Mbega yiyumvira yuko ata n’umwe amubona
  90,8,Mbega ntitwamuhaye amaso abiri
  90,9,N’ururimi hamwe n’iminwa ibiri
  90,10,Tumwereka inzira zose uko ari zibiri
  90,11,Mbega yarawusatuye uwo musozi
  90,12,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musozi
  90,13,N’uguha umushumvyi uburenganzira bwiwe n’iteka rimukwiye
  90,14,Canke ukamurisha k’umusi w’ikigoyi
  90,15,Impfuvyi y’umugenzi n’iyitari iyumugenzi
  90,16,Canke umukene ataco yifashije
  90,17,"Hanyuma\tabe\tmubemeye\tImana\tyiwe\ty’ukuri,\tnukuburirana ukwihangana nukuburirana mukugiriranira ikigongwe"
  90,18,Abo nibo bantu bo kuruhande rw’amahoro
  90,19,"Mugabo abahakanye amajambo yacu matagatifu, abo nibo bantu bo kuruhande rw’ishari"
  90,20,Umuriro wugarijwe kumpande zose uzoba uri hejuru yabo
  91,1,Ndarahiye kw’Izuba no kumishwarara yaryo
  91,2,No k’Ukwezi kugu kurikira
  91,3,No k’Umutaga uku boneshereza
  91,4,No kw’Ijoro mugihe kuripfuse
  91,5,No ku Majuru hamwe n’uwayubatse
  91,6,No kw’Isi hamwe n’uwayishashe
  91,7,No k’umutima hamwe n’uwawuringanije
  91,8,Hanyuma arawubwira amabi y’awo n’ivyiza vyawo
  91,9,Ntankeka arafise intsinzi uwasukuye umutima wiwe
  91,10,Kandi ntankeka yarahomvye uwa cinyije umutima wiwe
  91,11,Ba Thamuda barahakanye Umuremyi wabo kubera ukuzimira kwabo
  91,12,Mugihe yahagarara umwe mubabisha babo mukuru
  91,13,"Aho niho intumwa y’Imana yababwira iti:- iyi n’Ingamiya y’Imana ni muyireke hamwe n’ibinyobwa vyayo"
  91,14,"Mugabo barayihakanye iyo ntumwa y’Imana barayica, kuri ivyo rero Umuremyi wabo aca arabahonya kubera ibicumuro vyabo nukuba hanagura burundu"
  91,15,Kandi ntibatinya ingaruka yavyo
  92,1,Ndarahiye kw’Ijoro ripfuka ibintu vyose
  92,2,No k’Umutaga utanga umuco wayo
  92,3,No kuwaremye ikigabo n’ikigore
  92,4,Yuko ibikorwa vyanyu bitandukanye
  92,5,Umwe atanga nugutinya Imana yiwe
  92,6,N’ukwemera ijambo ryiza
  92,7,Tuzo mworohereza inzira yukuja mw’ijuru
  92,8,N’uwigira ingumyi ntiyiteho kubindi biremwa nkawe
  92,9,N’uguhakana ibintu vyiza
  92,10,Tuzo mworohereza inzira y’ukuja muriro udahera
  92,11,N’amatungo yiwe ntaco azomumarira mugihe azoba ariko aranyikira mu muriro udahera
  92,12,Mu vy’ukuri nikuri twebwe kuba menyesha ibiremwa vyose inzira nziza hamwe n’inzira y’ishari
  92,13,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turafise Ijuru n’Isi
  92,14,Rero nimugabe n’umuriro udahera waka n’inguvu nyinshi cane
  92,15,Ntawuzo winjira mwo atari umuntu mubi
  92,16,Ariwe ahakana n’ukuyiha umugongo iyi dini y’ukuri
  92,17,"Nuwu\tgamburukira\tImana\tyiwe\ty’ukuri\tazokingirwa\tnuwo\tmuriro udahera"
  92,18,Uwutanga amatungo yiwe kugira ngo yisukure
  92,19,Mugihe ata n’umwe yamugiriye ineza kugira ngo abe aramuriha iyo neza
  92,20,Atari ukurondera impuhwe z’Umuremyi wiwe mutagatifu
  92,21,Rero azoronka ikizo muhumuriza
  93,1,Ndarahiye k’Umutaga
  93,2,No kw’Ijoro riba rikwiragiye hose
  93,3,"Ntiyagusize Umuremyi wawe, canke ntiyashavuye"
  93,4,Ntankeka mugihe kiza kizoba ari ciza kuri wewe gusumba icabaye
  93,5,N’Umuremyi wawe azoguha vyinshi kugeza aho uzoshima
  93,6,Mbega nti yagusanze uri impfuvyi ica iguha uburaro n’uburamuko bwiza
  93,7,Igusanga utazi kurongora inzira nayo irakurongora
  93,8,Igusanga uri umukene iguha n’ubutunzi
  93,9,Rero ntubonere impfuvyi
  93,10,Kandi ntukankamire uwukubajije
  93,11,N’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe uyivuge